  "style": "APA",
  "texts": [
    "This dataset is intended to provide a detailed understanding of the interplay between visual content and its emotional effect on people, as well as natural language explanations for the emotional choice.",
    "The dataset consists of 455 K emotion attributions and explanations from humans, on around 80 K artworks, including more than 25 painting styles from more than 1000 painters.",
    "In addition, other previous works 7, 8 provided valuable question answering datasets related to cultural heritage and art.",
    "For example, VISCOUNTH 7 offers 6.5 M question-and-answer pairs using visual content and an associated natural language description.",
    "While the dataset boasts a wealth of cultural heritage information that could greatly benefit visitors to museums and cultural sites, it notably lacks dialogues."
  ],
  "correct_citations": [
    "In addition, other previous works 7, 8 provided valuable question answering datasets related to cultural heritage and art."
  ]
